Blanchette Brunoy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blanchette_Brunoy 0 Blanchette Brunoy (5 October 1915 – 3 April 2005) was a French actress. She was born Blanche Bilhaud in Paris as the daughter of a physician, and died in Manosque, Alpes-de-Haute-Provence of old age.
